title: The celebrity childhood pictures that will make your day
text:
The celebrity childhood pictures that will make your day 
Daily Mail Friday 23rd October, 2015 
We have all got an embarrassing childhood photo complete with terrible haircut, goofy teeth and horrendous outfit gathering dust in the loft never to see the light of day again - unless our mother has anything to do with it....
